import React from 'react'

import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

import {
  ReactComponent as Logo
} from '../../assets/fake-logo.svg'

import {
  HeaderContainer,
  OptionsContainer
} from './header.styles'

const Header = () => (
  <HeaderContainer>
    <Link 
      to='/'
      className='logo-container'
    >
      <Logo />
    </Link>
    <OptionsContainer>
      <Link 
        to='/shop'
        className='option'
      >
        Shop
      </Link>
      <Link 
        to='/contact'
        className='option'
      >
        Contact
      </Link>
      <Link 
        to='/signin'
        className='option'
      >
        Sign In
      </Link>
    </OptionsContainer>
  </HeaderContainer>
)

export default Header
